No. 818,

Misc.

Tyler v. California. Petitioner pro se. Stanley Mosk, Attorney General of California, Arlo E. Smith, Chief Assistant Attorney General, and John S. Mclnerny and Deraid E. Granberg, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondent.

District Court of Appeal of California, First Appellate District. Cer-tiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
